Package: ankiR
Title: Read and Analyze 'Anki' Flashcard Databases
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("Christos", "Longros", email = "chris.longros@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Read and analyze 'Anki' flashcard collection databases. Provides 
    functions to access notes, cards, decks, note types, and review logs from 
    'Anki' 'SQLite' databases with a tidy interface. Includes comprehensive
    analytics for learning progress, retention rates, and review patterns.
    Supports 'FSRS' (Free Spaced Repetition Scheduler) parameters including 
    stability, difficulty, and retrievability for advanced spaced repetition
    analysis. Features search functionality similar to Anki's browser,
    media file management, and data export capabilities.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
